WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Next, you should be in the garden for a while until the return of the Prince.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Lord Genzo, you always have a red face even though it's cold.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
I'm not drinking, so I'm red.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.000
I don't drink, but I'm always red.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.000
No, don't get angry.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Are you a shima-zu or a satsuma?

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.000
No, I'm a shima-osa.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.000
No, you're wrong.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.000
When you laugh, your face is a shima-ma.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.000
I don't think your face is a shima-ma.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.000
You're just a little kid.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.000
Anyway, you're a bad boy.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:54.000
You're a bad boy.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Next, you should be in the garden for a while until the return of the Prince.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Lord Genzo, you always have a red face even though it's cold.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:28.000
You're in the dark sky.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:39.000
You're waiting for someone to return.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:47.000
The leaves are disappearing.

00:01:47.000 --> 00:02:00.000
The winter is cold.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:11.000
The mountains are getting thinner with the light.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:17.000
The earth is crumbling.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:29.000
The poor people are dying.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:33.000
The sound of the bell is gone.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.000
It's getting dark.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:42.000
The Prince is not coming back yet.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:45.000
Please wait a little longer.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.000
What should I do?

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:49.000
I know you're a prince.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:54.000
I'll give you a lot of snow.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
Please wait a little longer.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.000
The Prince is coming.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:02.000
Wait a minute.

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:05.000
Please wait a little longer.

